c: 28
v: 76
t: "Inene u’Karûn (uKora) waye engowabantu bakuloMûsâ, kodwa wabaphatha kakubi. Kananjalo Samnika oovimba abazitshixo zabo zazithwalwa lihlokondiba lamadoda anamandla; ke kaloku abantu bakhe (izizalwana zakhe) bathi kuye: “Musa ukuzikhukhumalisa. Inene uAllâh Akabathandi abakhukhumeleyo"